    "text": "Daniel Loeb’s Third Point LLC ratcheted up the pressure on Nestlé SA, saying its business portfolio needs to be further simplified.\nNestlé has already taken a number of steps recommended by Mr. Loeb, an activist investor who built up a stake in the consumer-goods company last year. But Mr. Loeb, in a letter to Third Point investors on Monday, said Nestlé could make more changes, including selling its skin-health business. He also repeated a call for Nestlé to sell its large stake in cosmetics giant L’Oréal SA.\n... ",
